---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="bg-ink text-bg pt-16 pb-8 mt-24">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 pb-10 border-b border-bg/15 mb-6">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="inline-block mb-4">
          <img src="/logo-white.png" alt="India's Best AI Tools" class="h-20 md:h-24 w-auto" width="1043" height="844" style="aspect-ratio: 1043 / 844;" />
        </a>
        <p class="text-sm text-bg/70 max-w-md mb-5 leading-relaxed">
          An independent review journal for AI tools, with INR pricing, GST included, and payment workflows that actually work for Indian users.
        </p>
        <form
          id="newsletter"
          name="newsletter"
          method="POST"
          data-netlify="true"
          netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
          action="/thanks/"
          class="flex max-w-sm"
        >
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="newsletter" />
          <p class="hidden"><label>Don't fill this: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>
          <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-bg/10 border-2 border-bg/20 border-r-0 rounded-l-full text-bg text-sm placeholder:text-bg/50 focus:outline-none focus:border-yellow" />
          <button type="submit" class="px-5 py-3 border-2 border-pink bg-pink text-white rounded-r-full font-bold text-sm hover:bg-yellow hover:text-ink hover:border-yellow transition-colors">Subscribe</button>
        </form>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-yellow mb-4">By profession</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/for/freelancers/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Freelancers</a></li>
          <li><a href="/for/creators/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Creators</a></li>
          <li><a href="/for/cas/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">CAs &amp; Finance</a></li>
          <li><a href="/for/engineers/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Engineers</a></li>
          <li><a href="/for/teachers/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Teachers</a></li>
          <li><a href="/for/doctors/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Doctors</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-xs font-extrabold uppercase tracking-wider text-yellow mb-4">Tool reviews</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/tools/chatgpt-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">ChatGPT India</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/claude-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Claude India</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/gemini-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Gemini India</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/notion-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Notion India</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/canva-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Canva India</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/perplexity-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Perplexity India</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/copilot-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Copilot India</a></li>
          <li><a href="/tools/midjourney-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Midjourney India</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-3 text-xs text-bg/55 mb-3">
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-5 gap-y-2">
        <li><a href="/about/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">About</a></li>
        <li><a href="/methodology/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Methodology</a></li>
        <li><a href="/pricing-in-inr/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">All INR pricing</a></li>
        <li><a href="/guides/pay-for-ai-tools-india/" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">How to pay</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:hello@indiasbestaitools.com" class="text-bg/85 hover:text-yellow">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start gap-3 text-xs text-bg/55">
      <p>&copy; {year} India's Best AI Tools &middot; Independent review journal.</p>
      <p class="max-w-md md:text-right">
        Affiliate disclosure, we may earn a commission when you sign up via some links on this site, at no extra cost to you. Full <a href="/methodology/" class="text-yellow underline">methodology &amp; editorial policy</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
